gmd:title.gco:CharacterString: CV16036 Shallow Sub-Seabed Seismic Stratigraphic Survey

gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: This shallow sub-seabed seismic stratigraphic survey, led by University College Cork (UCC), on board the Marine Institute's R.V. Celtic Voyager, was to be conducted in the Celtic Sea. However, the survey was aborted and objectives not completed.
